  p We detected that you have multiple Pizza 42 accounts with the email address <strong>#{email}</strong>.

  p Would you like to link these accounts together? This will allow you to log in with any of your authentication methods and access the same profile and order history.

  .info-box
    p <strong>Security Notice:</strong>
    p To verify your identity, you'll be asked to re-authenticate with your other login method. This ensures that only you can link these accounts together.

  .info-box
    p <strong>Primary Account:</strong> <code>#{primaryUserId}</code>
    p <strong>Account to Link:</strong> <code>#{secondaryUserId}</code>

  .button-container
    form(method='GET', action=`https://${auth0Domain}/authorize`, style='display: inline-block;')
      input(type='hidden', name='client_id', value=clientId)
      input(type='hidden', name='response_type', value='code')
      input(type='hidden', name='redirect_uri', value=redirectUri)
      input(type='hidden', name='scope', value='openid profile email')
      input(type='hidden', name='state', value=continuationToken)
      input(type='hidden', name='prompt', value='login')
      button.button(type='submit') âœ“ Link Accounts

  .button-container
    a.button.button-secondary(href=appUrl) âœ— Cancel

  p(style='font-size: 12px; color: #78716c; text-align: center; margin-top: 24px;')
    | By linking accounts, your user data and order history will be merged.
